room_title: Escape room "Chapter Three: The Morgue" by Evil Genius Escape Rooms in Los Angeles
room_address: 2525 W. Washington Blvd. Los Angeles, CA 90018
room_description:
It is hard to escape the feeling of finality when standing in a place where bodies get prepared for their eternal rest. All of your decisions have lead you to this point, yet it hardly feels like you had a choice. You were destined to be here.
You enter the morgue, which has obviously been abandoned for some time. Ivy crawls along the walls, the pipes drip, leaves and dead bugs litter the floor. And that smell.
You wait in the dark knowing that there is something, or maybe someone, out there. Your final test...
